data.description: This clean, move-in ready home is a great find with NEW carpet & laminate flooring! Offering 3 bedrooms, 2 baths & 2 car garage, this single story has a spacious living room with floor to ceiling brick fireplace! Great counter space in kitchen with breakfast bar overlooking living. Master suite offers dual sinks. Secondary bedrooms have beautiful new laminate wood floors. Walking distance to elementary school! Close to Fish Creek Linear Park, Joe Pool Lake & numerous shopping & dining options. Easy access to 360 & I-20!
